It is no more news that FFK releases various kind of tweets daily in his official twitter account. Femi Fani-Kayode who is also known FFK is not a new name among Nigerians and he remains a prominent person in Nigeria. FFK is known for his vocal way of life and he is not always afraid to say whatever comes to his mind. READ ALSO: Governance and evaluation of Ex-Minister Femi Fani-Kayode Faux Pas Recently, he released series of tweets in his official twitter account. Those tweets have gotten various reactions on twitter. “Your Power Is Nothing And Real Men Don’t Just Threaten, They Act And They Strike” – FFK made this statement in his official twitter page few hours ago.